overview:
Wiki Cream is a new site where you can create and edit your own pages about your business or yourself.

Unlike other sites and Wiki projects your can add your business information regardless of the size or nature of it. In the past smaller and less conventional businesses have struggled to get onto some other sites due to their guidelines. We believe that no matter your business model or size there should be an independent place for your business to be listed.
